===Etymology===
From ''[[Gespräch|Gesprächs]]+[[Partikel|partikel]]'', literally ''[[conversation]] [[particle]]''.

===Pronunciation===
*Ge·sprächs·par·ti·kel(n)
*{{Unicode|/ɡəʃprɛ:çspartikəl/}}, ''Plural:'' {{Unicode|/ɡəʃprɛ:çspartikəln/}}

# [[interjection]], a [[particle]] without an actual meaning, which is used in a [[conversation]].

